***********Alter (to change the schema) ***************
1) **ADD Column** 
    ALTER TABLE table_name 
    ADD COLUMN column_name datatype constraint;
# EXAMPLE -:
mysql> ALTER TABLE student
    -> ADD COLUMN age INT ;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.10 sec)
Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0
